OL,5, Millions of people will pay an extra   
OL,6, #693 a year on their energy bills from 
OL,7, April, a rise of 54%, Ofgem has said.  
OL,9,FThe regulator's new price limit means  
OL,10,F18 million households in England, Wales
OL,11,Fand Scotland will typically pay #1,971 
OL,12,Fa year for gas and electricity.        
OL,14,FAnother 4.5 million people on          
OL,15,Fprepayment meters will see an even     
OL,16,Fbigger increase of #708 a year.        
OL,18,FChancellor Rishi Sunak has outlined    
OL,19,Fplans to soften the blow via council   
OL,20,Ftax rebates and help with bills.       
